This privacy policy (“
Privacy Policy
”) describes the information, including personal information, collected by TheoremReach Inc., (“we” or “our” or “us”), including our affiliates and subsidiaries, how we collect that information, how that information may be used, and with whom it may be shared when you use our Services (as defined below).
When we use the term “personal information”, we mean information that can be used to identify you.
References to “you” or “your” means the person accessing the Website and/or using our Services.
This Privacy Policy applies to your use of http://theoremreach.com (the “Website”), participation in our surveys, or using other products or services we may provide (collectively, the “Services”) and information, including personal information, you may provide to us via the Website, the Services, including, without limitation, information you provide in our Website chat feature, or information, including personal information, you provide to us via email or telephone. If you do not agree with this Privacy Policy, then you must not access or use the Services.
